      <Breadcrumbs links={links} />
      
      <div class="glass-effect rounded-lg p-8 mt-6">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-black/80 dark:text-white/80">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p>By accessing and using this website, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provisions of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by these terms, please do not use this website.</p>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white mb-3">2. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>The content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and images, is the property of Prodipta Roy and is protected by copyright laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from this content without express written consent.</p>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white mb-3">3. User Conduct</h2>
            <p>You agree to use this website only for lawful purposes and in a way that does not infringe upon the rights of others or restrict their use of the website.</p>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white mb-3">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p>This website is provided on an "as is" basis. Prodipta Roy makes no warranties, expressed or implied, and hereby disclaims all warranties, including without limitation, implied warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement.</p>
          </section>
          
